My Portfolio

iOS Developer - UI/UX - Modeling - Backend

PROJECTS

Donation Finder

This app concept helps to find different donation/recycling centers/bins/etc. in an easy to use map with easy identification of the specific donation/recycling option.

Special Order Keeper

This is a small basic app I created for a friend that wanted to keep track of special orders of jewelry that he was doing. Nothing fancy.

Pirates Booty Drop

My first game. A clone of a standard 2D drop & merge style game. This one was fun!

Putt Putt Golf Scorecard

A fun golf putting scorecard made specifically for my favorite local putting green. It features a map selection of all the deferent locations they have with specifics for each hole on the courses. Allowing for customization and updating of all the current holes at each course for the business. And also a standard non-specific way of using the scorecard for use at any putting course anywhere!

Line-ize

Line-ize is on the App Store! Available for both iPhone & iPad. It is a quick and easy way to turn images and photos into line drawings for easier use for whatever your need may be. Multiple filters to try with adjustments. This app has been on the App Store since 2020.

ABOUT

Hello! I'm Kevin and I'm an iOS Developer. I have experience using many popular frameworks of the iOS ecosystem. I've been using the Swift programming language since the second iteration and love to stay up to date with all the fun new stuff that Apple adds each year. I've also been using SwiftUI since its inception, being that I believe that the declarative way of UI is the future.

I particularly love doing UX/UI aspects of iOS but I am well versed in many of Apple's API's. I'm new to the workforce of programming and development but that should not be confused with my abilities and experience in the iOS ecosystem at large. I love a good challenge and have confidence in my ability to tackle tasks in areas that I may have not used before or are a little less familiar with. I'm exceptionally resourceful and good at time management.
